809
00:56:27,009 --> 00:56:28,010
Aku tidak!

810
00:56:28,135 --> 00:56:29,428
Aku bersikap pintar.

811
00:56:29,553 --> 00:56:31,764
Jangan mendekati jendela.

812
00:56:32,681 --> 00:56:33,432
Ayo bergerak.

813
00:57:40,666 --> 00:57:41,876
Ia masih dekat.

814
00:57:44,003 --> 00:57:45,920
