- Pergi, pergi! - Pergi, pergi.

819
00:58:52,363 --> 00:58:53,530
Ava, Ava!

820
00:58:53,656 --> 00:58:54,406
Ava! Ava!

821
00:59:11,340 --> 00:59:12,925
Ia menunggu.

822
00:59:13,050 --> 00:59:14,843
Ia menunggu sampai dia sendirian.

823
