893
01:05:38,060 --> 01:05:39,436
Apa itu tadi!

894
01:05:41,605 --> 01:05:42,481
Bagus.

895
01:05:42,606 --> 01:05:43,357
Tunggu!

896
01:05:54,326 --> 01:05:55,827
