900
01:06:35,492 --> 01:06:37,160
Ia datang.

901
01:06:37,285 --> 01:06:38,078
Merunduk!

902
01:06:40,580 --> 01:06:41,415
Pergi, pergi!

903
01:06:45,669 --> 01:06:47,170
